Deep linking behavior:

When user clicks “Open in Protocol Builder”, redirect to Protocol Builder with a prefilled query state or session payload.

The builder must open with input data that make the protocol clinically coherent.

Implement route:
 /protocol-builder?template=<template_id>&prefill=<encoded_payload>

Or equivalent state-based navigation if needed.

Each featured protocol must include a recommended prefill payload.

